    .row 
      .image.large-6.columns

      .text.large-6.columns
        h3 Members
        p Your community recieves the messages via the mobile application, sms and or email. Making communication simple and efficient.
        h5  Email and Sms options 
        p If some of your recipients prefer to receive messages by sms or email, you can use Ziviso’s in-built sms and email options to allow you to communicate with your customers and members in a way that suits them.
